summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2006 JEEP LIBERTY. THE CONTACT RECEIVED NOTIFICATION OF NHTSA CAMPAIGN NUMBER: 13V252000 (FUEL SYSTEM, GASOLINE, STRUCTURE). THE VEHICLE WAS TAKEN TO THE DEALER (AL SERRA JEEP, CHRYSLER IN GRAND BLANC, MICHIGAN) WHO STATED THAT THE RECALL REPAIRS COULD NOT BE PERFORMED DUE TO EXCESSIVE CORROSION OF THE FRAME. THE DEALER REFERRED THE CONTACT TO NHTSA. THE MANUFACTURER WAS NOT MADE AWARE OF THE FAILURE. THE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 169,000.
